dc_title_s: Professor Pathfinder's Princeton : Princeton University, greater Princeton street map
dc_description_s: Recto: Professor Pathfinder's Princeton University and central Princeton (1:6,850). Inset map: Nasssau Street and Central Business District. Verso: Greater Princeton area street map (1:25,000). Princeton University map shows generalized land use and major buildings color-coded by function. Princeton University map shows generalized land use and major buildings color-coded by function. Panel title. Includes text, indexes, inset of "Nassau Street and central business district", coverage map, specimen map, and col. ill.
